These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
City: berlin, boston, colone, new-york
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, polish, chinese, malaysian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, marigold, azalea, zinnia
 1. the polish is not to the right of the russian##8
 2. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person who growsdaisy##8
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the russian is not to the left of the malaysian##8
 5. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the malaysian##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who growsmarigold and the polish##2
 9. the person who growszinnia is the person watching family movies##1
10. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
11. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8
14. the person traveling to boston is the person who growsazalea##1
15. the person traveling to boston is not the polish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City         | berlin     | boston   | new-york | colone |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Nationality         | polish  | chinese  | malaysian  | russian |
| Flower     | daisy    | azalea | marigold     | zinnia    |

