.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, aristoff, old-henry, swisher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, november, may
City: colone, san-francisco, rome, liverpool
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person traveling to colone and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 5. the person traveling to colone is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 6. the swisher-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
 8. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
11. the person traveling to colone is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
14. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
18. the aristoff-smoker is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Cigar          | swisher     | aristoff | game | old-henry  |
| Birthday   | april    | november  | may | january |
| City           | rome | liverpool | colone    | san-francisco  |

