.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
House: gothic-revival, wooden, victorian, futuristic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, folk, jazz
4 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 2. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
 3. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 4. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 6. the futuristic house is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| House         | gothic-revival    | futuristic   | victorian | wooden |
| Beverage   | tea     | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate   | iced-tea      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | folk      | jazz       |
| Pet         | goldfish    | hamster | rabbit   | mouse    |

