.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, purple, amber, lavender
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, dubstep, classical, blues
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, tulip, zinnia
 1. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
 2. the fan of blues is the person who likes purple##1
 3. the person who growsrose is not the person who likes blood-red##6
 4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the fan of classical##8
 6. the person who growstulip is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person who growsrose is not to the left of the person who likes purple##8
 8. the fan of dubstep is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the fan of soul is not to the left of the person who likes lavender##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person who growszinnia is between the person who likes lavender and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
13. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Color         | lavender     | blood-red | amber   | purple  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | disaster   | drama     | mystery  |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | classical     | dubstep | blues  |
| Flower         | tulip     | zinnia | iris   | rose |

