 5. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
11. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
13. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
