 4. the person eating radish is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to hamburg##7
 9. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating onion is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
11. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
12. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
13. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to marseilles##1
14. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
16. the person eating onion is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8

