15. the palace house is the person who likes yellow##1
16. the tower house is not to the right of the person who likes ebony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| House           | tower | palace       | art-deco      | modern  |
| Color   | mauve    | yellow | ebony   | ivory   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | r&b          | soul      | gospel  |
| Flower   | bellflower   | zinnia      | azalea | orchid |

